            "notes": "The deck focuses on utilizing powerful reanimation spells and creatures to quickly overwhelm the opponent with aggressive threats. By efficiently leveraging cards like Unburial Rites, Exhume, and Necromancy, as well as powerful creatures like Griselbrand and Iona, the deck aims to put pressure on the opponent early and often. The inclusion of disruption spells like Thoughtseize and Inquisition of Kozilek helps to disrupt the opponent's game plan and clear the way for your threats to come through. Additionally, the deck is rounded out with versatile removal spells like Swords to Plowshares and Fatal Push to deal with opposing threats. The goal is to establish a dominant board presence and close out the game quickly."
